            <pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 13:03:40 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>0.9.12</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.9.12</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.2</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>Sparkle integration + Soniox streaming + audio hardening</h3>
                <p>Foundational release — transitioning to the Sparkle update framework.</p>
                <ul>
                <li>Soniox upload now streams from disk (no RAM spike on long meetings)</li>
                <li>Retry with exponential backoff on transient network errors</li>
                <li>Upload progress UI</li>
                <li>Mic config-change handling (AirPods, USB, device swap)</li>
                <li>Lid-close now stops recording cleanly</li>
                <li>Fewer silent I/O failures</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
